{{!--
=============================================================================
PAGE TEMPLATE - Static Pages
=============================================================================

Displays static pages (About, Contact, etc.).
Similar to posts but without author/date meta.

FEATURES:
- Optional title/feature image (Beta editor setting)
- Cleaner layout than posts (no author card, tags)

CSS CLASSES (see assets/css/custom.css §8):
- .page.outer: Page wrapper
- .page-header: Title section
- .gh-content: Main content area

SPECIAL PAGE TEMPLATES:
Pages with specific slugs use custom templates:
- /essays/  → page-essays.hbs
- /stories/ → page-stories.hbs
- /notes/   → page-notes.hbs
- /sketches/ → page-sketches.hbs
--}}
{{!< default}}

{{#post}}
<article class="page {{page_class}} outer{{#match @page.show_title_and_feature_image "!=" true}} no-title{{/match}}">
    <div class="inner">
        {{#match @page.show_title_and_feature_image}}
        <header class="page-header">
            <h1 class="page-title">{{title}}</h1>
            
            {{#if feature_image}}
                <figure class="page-feature-image">
                    <img 
                        src="{{img_url feature_image size="l"}}" 
                        alt="{{#if feature_image_alt}}{{feature_image_alt}}{{else}}{{title}}{{/if}}"
                        loading="eager"
                    >
                </figure>
            {{/if}}
        </header>
        {{/match}}
        
        <section class="gh-content page-content">
            {{content}}
        </section>
    </div>
</article>
{{/post}}
